cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual scene understanding and relationship prediction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper introduces a new model for few-shot learning, which is a common topic in AI research. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper introduces a new graph convolution framework for training the model. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper deals with natural language predicates and their relationship to visual scenes. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with visual scene understanding and the use of object representations.
